{"tid":1222194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：台方拒引渡陳同佳七月死線已不存在","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T00:50:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10397022d328d763da1ec7aa667489f8541c520a","tid":1222194,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政會議成員湯家驊表示，不想再見到有流血事件發生，而台灣方面已表明條例通過後亦不會引渡陳同佳，七月死線已不存在，政府可以考慮其他方法解決目前困局。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊表示，對逃犯條例修訂引發大規模衝突感到心痛，他承認政府低估了社會對修例的反響，他認為目前要做的是避免再有流血事件發生，而七月通過修例的死線已不存在。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議召集人陳智思認為，政府需盤算如何處理以免加劇對立，但他未有直接回應應否急於在本屆會期內處理。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員林健鋒亦認為政府應想辦法避免加劇衝突。"},{"pid":"bb6918da79622680fe3e09246552fe27b010146e","tid":1222194,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/H0bud7TwWEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH0bud7TwWEQ&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3Pjc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=4cc37b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H0bud7TwWEQ</a>"},{"pid":"458111156614b8a72612f42e3e3bf3cc5e92e29e","tid":1222194,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=351755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351755&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3Pjc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=f3ff5fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351755&h=906a4dc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=351755</a>"},{"pid":"23d872f43684ee4f81062ff2e8ac5a9b6e088fb6","tid":1222194,"uid":28547,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"你老闆而家先表態！<br />\n暈撚左成個禮拜呀！"},{"pid":"6ed6060198c864be0929fc4efc463b1c8e20cac7","tid":1222194